      { q: "What is included in the Bosphorus dinner cruise price?", a: "All shared dinner packages include hotel pickup and drop-off support, the evening Bosphorus route, dinner service, and the live entertainment program. The exact beverage inclusion depends on the package: Silver Soft focuses on soft drinks, Silver Alcoholic adds local alcoholic drinks, Gold Soft keeps the premium tier without alcohol, and Gold Unlimited Alcohol is the fullest drinks package." },
      { q: "How long is the dinner cruise?", a: "The cruise lasts approximately 3.5 hours on the water. Including hotel transfers, the entire experience takes about 5 hours from pickup to drop-off." },
      { q: "Is alcohol included in the dinner cruise?", a: "Alcohol is included in the alcoholic dinner tiers, not in the soft-drinks tiers. Silver Alcoholic includes local alcoholic drinks, while Gold Unlimited Alcohol is the highest beverage tier on the shared product." },
      { q: "Can I celebrate a birthday or anniversary on the dinner cruise?", a: "Yes! Inform us when booking and we can arrange a cake, special table decoration, and a celebratory announcement. These extras are often complimentary." }
